Ranger Help for: run
====================

SYNTAX:      run <dir> [dir] [dir] ...
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     5 per room
SKILL TYPE:  cartography

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to sprint through multiple rooms in quick
succession by specifying a series of directions. The Ranger moves
rapidly through each room without stopping, costing 5 SP per room
traversed. This is useful for covering long distances quickly or
fleeing from danger. The Ranger cannot stop mid-run and may be
interrupted by obstacles, locked doors, or aggressive creatures.
